Black First Land First (BLF) has been deregistered as a political party by the Electoral Commission of South Africa (ECSA) on the instruction of the racist whites only Freedom Front Plus (FF+). A Special Policy Conference, to find a way forward for BLF, shall be held under the following details: Date: 30 November 209
Time: 08:00
Venue: Denis Hurley Centre
